No. 630. Harry Dodd, Trustee, etc., Petitioner, v. A. Samel and S. Saul. April 9, 1906. Mr. Alex. C. King andrMV. Benjamin Z. Phillips for petitioner. Mr. Victor Smith for respondents.

Petition for a writ-of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
